Author : wujl
Date : 20170105
Description :
    This is a demo which communicate with client and server by using socket;
    Several types being used in this demo : block, NoBlock, MultiPlexing(select/pool/epool), and others;
    
Definations:
    Client and server will use IP 127.0.0.1;
    Client use port 8081, server use port 8082;

V1.0.1:
    Add unix udp mode for test;
    wujl, 20170223;

